title:
['Statue of Bodhisattva at Dalada Maluwa of Polonnaruwa – බෝධිසත්ව පිලිමය']

Rating:
['1', '5.00']

Content:

Statue of bodhisattva
This statue lies in the center of the 
 at a slightly elevated ground. The arms of the statue are missing.  It is unclear whether this is a statue of King Nissanga Malla (1187-1196)  or a bodhisattva.
Note that some locations marked by Google Maps in around this area is wrong.
